name: Rupantalwar.myonepageapp
tagline: A sleek Android single-page app that boasts dynamic tiles UI Design
body:
### My One Page App.
This is a simple one-page Android application that consists of a sleek tile-like UI design. The tiles contain swipe gesture recognizers and click listeners that makes them user interactive.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
